_sText:
This is a prison break map with an escape theme to it. you can still do all of your usual activities ie footie, swimming, disco etc but if you want to escape to freedom you need to pass 3 hard tests first, get past that and you can launch a nuke or you can just grab a gun and kill anything that moves!

unlike the usual prison maps there are no buttons for the cell doors they are on a timer set to open withing 1 minute of the map starting, giving ct's a chance to get into position and to stop all the whining terrorists!

Thanks to Westsid3r for the nuke
